title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Alphet Wit Da Tiddies Out
description:
What are you really worth? This week, Jimmy and Larry are getting an early start to bring you the best private sale of the summer, what constitutes a vacation, the best color for underwear, a nipple self-assessment, loud shoes, Pitti Uomo FOMO, Kanye West story time Italian style, the alphabet of slurs, a seasonal surge in TF hate, recasting the main character of TikTok, drug hardos, the stalking IRL to bullied URL pipeline, Moneyball date night sabermetrics, conversing with women like it’s a podcast, the best sandwiches in the game right now, applying architectural principles to your lunch, cold cut labias, a smorgasboard of big brain food takes, wholesome ice cream talk inspired by the king of soft serve and much more.
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
